{
  "text": "Here we provide a summary of the xDAWN algorithm; more details can be found in [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . xDAWN is a spatial filtering algorithm designed to enhance the ERP through maximizing the signal to signal plus noise ratio (SSNR). The result of this algorithm are the spatial filters U , which are ranked in terms of their SSNR. The EEG signal X is decomposed into three parts as:",
